Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.70,00:00:07.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,An errand?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.83,00:00:09.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.37,00:00:12.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A lot of fortune-telling work has come in all of a sudden,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.25,00:00:16.08,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,so I'd like you to go in my stead \Nto pick up the items I ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.45,00:00:17.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,00:00:18.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You can count on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,00:00:21.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll give this errand my all!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,00:00:24.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Tell me, tell me! What'd you order?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.12,00:00:28.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's an import I've wanted for a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.37,00:00:31.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to use it to tell fortunes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,00:00:34.75,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,It's called... the Chinese Porcelain Bowl \Nwith Bats and Nine Peaches!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.45,00:00:34.75,Caption,,0,0,0,,CHINESE PORCELAIN BOWL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.45,00:00:34.75,Caption2,,0,0,0,,WITH BATS AND NINE PEACHES
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.75,00:00:37.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Chinese Porcelain Bowl with Bats and Nine Peaches?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,00:00:39.87,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Does it have some sort of legendary \Nfortune-telling power or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.87,00:00:41.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,00:00:47.25,Caption,,0,0,0,,Crystal Fortunes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,00:00:47.25,Caption2,,0,0,0,,ASTROLOGY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.21,00:00:47.25,Caption3,,0,0,0,,Kokkuri
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.21,00:00:47.25,Caption4,,0,0,0,,DANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.21,00:00:47.25,Caption5,,0,0,0,,FORTUNES
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.21,00:00:47.25,Caption6,,0,0,0,,TEAR READING
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.21,00:00:47.25,Caption7,,0,0,0,,DREAM FORTUNES
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.29,00:00:47.25,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, people lose their way \Nto their fate, or the crossroads of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.37,00:00:51.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,as they wander through the maze of their everyday lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,00:00:53.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In those times,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.83,00:00:56.29,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,a diviner can present you with an arrow \Npointing to the right choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.79,00:01:02.16,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,The magical power that points the way \Nis sometimes panacea, sometimes poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.62,00:01:06.91,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,To possess that power, one must be a girl \Nwho has passed her fifteenth birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.66,00:01:12.62,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,The girls in this fortune-telling town \Nare sometimes goddesses, sometimes witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,00:01:13.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Urara!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.00,00:01:19.12,Song,,0,0,0,,I want to make my dreams come true
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,00:01:21.87,Song,,0,0,0,,So I'll give it my all again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,00:01:27.95,Song,,0,0,0,,When I get lost, I'll ask the gods to help me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.95,00:01:31.91,Song,,0,0,0,,See, you can see a light! Which way? (That way!)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.08,00:01:35.25,Song,,0,0,0,,Believe in yourself and march on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.62,00:01:39.62,Song,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five, six! Jan-jan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,00:01:42.91,Song,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five, six! Jan-jan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,00:01:48.50,Song,,0,0,0,,Which way should I go? I can't decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,00:01:54.12,Song,,0,0,0,,The path to our dreams is always a big labyrinth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.62,00:01:57.45,Song,,0,0,0,,To the left? To the right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.62,00:02:00.37,Song,,0,0,0,,Which way is right? (Which way?)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,00:02:03.25,Song,,0,0,0,,No matter which way I go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,00:02:07.37,Song,,0,0,0,,It'll be fun because my friends are there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,00:02:09.45,Song,,0,0,0,,That's the right answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.45,00:02:12.37,Song,,0,0,0,,I want to make my dreams come true
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.37,00:02:15.25,Song,,0,0,0,,So I'll give it my all again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.25,00:02:20.95,Song,,0,0,0,,When I get lost, I'll ask the gods to help me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,00:02:27.00,Song,,0,0,0,,See, you can see the future! Let's walk together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,00:02:31.54,Song,,0,0,0,,See, you can see a smile! Which way? (This way!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,00:02:34.70,Song,,0,0,0,,Believe in yourself and march on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.95,00:02:38.95,Song,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five, six! Jan-jan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,00:02:42.16,Song,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five, six! Jan-jan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.66,00:02:46.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That looks yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,00:02:49.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Those clothes are so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,00:02:52.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come on, you two, don't get distracted!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,00:02:56.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We're never gonna get there at this rate-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,00:03:01.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's the divining instrument shop Benten.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,00:03:04.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Isn't it that famous store?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,00:03:09.12,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Umm, I heard it's the biggest \Ndivining tool shop in Meirocho,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,00:03:12.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and they sell any kind of implement that you might need.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.87,00:03:15.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That sounds cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,00:03:17.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It'd be fine if it were just cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.37,00:03:18.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,00:03:21.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I heard something a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,00:03:24.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Something about the shopkeeper at Benten Instruments.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,00:03:29.79,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,She uses the guise of an Urara \Nto control Meirocho from the shadows,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,00:03:32.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and she's involved in the black market, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,00:03:35.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And she's a really successful gambler, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,00:03:37.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She controls town from the shadows?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,00:03:39.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She's a successful gambler?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,00:03:40.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She goes by the name...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,00:03:42.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The Old Tanuki of Bloque Ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,00:03:44.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Old Tanuki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,00:03:48.87,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Did we just take on an errand \Nthat's gonna be a lot of trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,00:03:52.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Anyway, everyone, be extra careful to watch yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,00:03:54.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We didn't come here to play around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,00:03:55.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.12,00:03:57.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,00:04:00.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,By the way, why're we leashed together like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,00:04:04.33,Caption,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,00:04:04.33,Caption2,,0,0,0,,distractions!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,00:04:04.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If I don't do this, we'll never make it there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,00:04:07.16,Caption,,0,0,0,,Benten
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,00:04:07.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,00:04:14.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow, there are so many weird things here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,00:04:17.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,These are all divining tools?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.45,00:04:20.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I dunno what they're used for!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,00:04:22.62,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I heard the rumors, but she really does have \Nan amazing variety of items!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,00:04:24.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A lot of these I've only seen in books!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.75,00:04:27.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is a seeing stone, also called a Sun Stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,00:04:29.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's a stone that shows you the right path!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,00:04:31.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, look, rosemary incense!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,00:04:35.16,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,It's been used since the time of the Egyptian kings \Nand it has a powerful warding effect on spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,00:04:37.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They placed it inside pharaohs' tombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,00:04:39.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She even has an eyeball crystal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,00:04:41.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Kon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,00:04:44.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We didn't come here to play around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,00:04:47.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not playing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,00:04:49.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm just studying a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,00:04:56.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It... it's just that Old Tanuki's shop is so amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,00:05:00.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Who're you callin' a tanuki, you little fox?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,00:05:09.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm the owner of this shop, Benten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,00:05:11.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,00:05:13.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How're you gonna pay for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,00:05:16.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This eyeball crystal's an extremely rare item.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,00:05:18.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,00:05:22.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Think you can get out of it just by apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,00:05:26.33,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Should I go by the book \Nand make you pay with your body?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,00:05:27.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.75,00:05:28.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Go right ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,00:05:30.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.04,00:05:31.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why're you doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,00:05:35.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I meant you'll pay me back with physical labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,00:05:39.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come on. I've got mountains of work for you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,00:05:43.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We've got no choice but to do as Benten-san says.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,00:05:47.45,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Let's finish this work quick and \Ntake care of Nina-sensei's errand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,00:05:48.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,00:05:50.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Stop the chit-chat and change out of those clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,00:05:53.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,00:05:55.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is pretty fashionable!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,00:05:57.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm glad there isn't much fabric!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,00:05:59.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's really loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,00:06:02.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wh-why am I the only one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,00:06:03.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,00:06:04.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm so jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,00:06:07.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, that looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,00:06:10.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-I've never worn Western-style clothes before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.83,00:06:12.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,00:06:13.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,00:06:15.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,00:06:17.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,H-hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,00:06:19.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,00:06:22.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why do you have all these weird outfits?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,00:06:24.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Because my shop has everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,00:06:27.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What do these have to do with divining?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,00:06:32.33,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, what kind of fortune-telling \Ndo you do with these rocks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,00:06:35.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, those are flints.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,00:06:38.62,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,It's used less for fortune-telling \Nand more for protective spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,00:06:43.54,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,You strike the flint like this \Nto spread sparks and ward off spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,00:06:45.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My, that's amazing, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,00:06:48.37,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,You know so much about these things, \Ndespite being so young!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,00:06:50.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll be a promising Urara in the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,00:06:52.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,O-of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,00:06:55.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,you could always use it as a regular fire-starter,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,00:06:56.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but I recommend taking it with you on errands or trips
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,00:06:58.75,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Jeez, why is Kon the only one standing out so much? \Nbut I recommend taking it with you on errands or trips
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,00:06:59.87,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Jeez, why is Kon the only one standing out so much? \Nbecause you can also use it as a charm to ward off danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,00:07:00.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,because you can also use it as a charm to ward off danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,00:07:01.95,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Okay, I can stand out, too! \Nbecause you can also use it as a charm to ward off danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,00:07:04.45,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Gotta find something really flashy. \NFire gods are said to be the strongest at protecting the home,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,00:07:05.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,so sparks confer a cleansing power to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,00:07:07.04,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know this! \Nso sparks confer a cleansing power to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,00:07:10.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow, what's this book about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,00:07:12.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,00:07:14.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Can I help you find something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,00:07:19.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Everyone's doing such an amazing job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,00:07:21.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've gotta do something, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.41,00:07:24.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I'm not good with physical labor,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,00:07:28.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and I definitely can't approach customers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.75,00:07:30.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Be brave, Nono!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,00:07:32.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Matsuko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,00:07:34.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,00:07:37.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,00:07:39.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,W-welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,00:07:43.79,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Oh, I thought it was an employee, \Nbut it's just a wind-up doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,00:07:45.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It looks so real!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,00:07:46.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.33,00:07:49.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's touch it a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,00:07:50.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do not touch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,00:07:54.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,00:07:59.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How long is she going to make us work?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,00:08:02.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We've got to pick up the bowl and head home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,00:08:02.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Kon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,00:08:07.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why are you wearing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,00:08:09.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So Tanuki-san doesn't find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,00:08:11.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,00:08:15.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They're here, Koume!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,00:08:17.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, good work-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,00:08:17.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,00:08:21.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,One of you looks really shady right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,00:08:24.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What did you call us here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,00:08:27.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Look at this, Kon. I bet you'll be happy to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,00:08:30.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-is that Sendai Takao's sword?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.12,00:08:30.70,Caption,,0,0,0,,SENDAI TAKAO'S SWORD
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.83,00:08:35.45,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,It's a legendary item said to increase your divining power \Nby a thousand... maybe two thousand percent!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,00:08:37.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh? I didn't know it was that valuable!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,00:08:39.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And that's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,00:08:44.45,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,All the items I see here are powerful divining tools that \Nnormal Urara would never be able to get their hands on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,00:08:46.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,00:08:49.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait, Koume, why are you putting that on now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,00:08:50.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.08,00:08:54.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey! Why're you slacking off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.75,00:08:55.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She found us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,00:08:58.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see you're making light of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,00:09:00.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,W-we didn't mean to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,00:09:06.16,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I've already known for a while \Nthat you're the new students from Natsumeya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,00:09:09.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's Nina-sensei's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,00:09:10.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Not so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,00:09:15.08,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I'm holding on to this until \Nyou pay me back for that crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,00:09:16.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,00:09:19.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll have you work here for a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,00:09:20.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A year?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,00:09:24.08,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,We can't! I know it was expensive, \Nbut a year's way too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,00:09:27.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If we take a year off, we'll fail our Urara training!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,00:09:29.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We'll be exiled from Meirocho!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,00:09:31.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to work, then pay for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.66,00:09:32.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Or how about...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,00:09:36.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I take one of your eyes in exchange for that crystal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,00:09:40.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They're a rare red color, so I'm sure one will sell fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,00:09:43.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You... you big mean tanuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,00:09:45.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Chiya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,00:09:49.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What? You wanna go at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,00:09:52.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Benten-san, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,00:09:55.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But training is really important to an Urara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,00:09:57.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We have to get back to Natsumeya soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,00:10:00.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So please let us go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,00:10:04.45,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I don't care how many years it takes, \NI'll pay you back for the crystal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,00:10:08.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We can't throw away our training here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,00:10:11.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,P-please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,00:10:14.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright, why don't we play a game of chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,00:10:16.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Dice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,00:10:21.66,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,The rules are simple. Roll the dice, \Nand whoever has the highest result wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,00:10:25.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you win, you won't have to pay for the crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,00:10:28.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But if you lose, you'll work for me for three more years!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,00:10:29.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Three years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,00:10:33.62,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,It's not knowing how it'll turn out \Nthat makes the game interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,00:10:36.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Bet your futures on this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.04,00:10:39.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well? Wanna give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,00:10:41.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,00:10:44.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait, Chiya, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,00:10:46.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You'll lose for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,00:10:47.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,00:10:48.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Remember what Kon said?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,00:10:51.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Benten-san's a really successful gambler.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,00:10:54.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's right! It's really easy for her to manipulate the dice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,00:10:58.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But we won't know unless we try!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,00:11:02.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We don't know if we'll win or lose right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,00:11:07.29,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,But Benten-san, we're training \Nso we can face the unseen future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,00:11:11.70,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,So to keep training, we're gonna win \Nand go back to Natsumeya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,00:11:14.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright. It's all up to you, Chiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,00:11:15.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's in your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,00:11:17.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Roll well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,00:11:21.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Now, let's have at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,00:11:23.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,00:11:30.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Chiya got a four.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,00:11:32.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Benten-san's turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,00:11:39.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,H-hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,00:11:47.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You were close to never going back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,00:11:53.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Benten-san! See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,00:11:59.83,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,If you'd abandoned your studies over a little threat \Nlike that and run away from a challenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.83,00:12:02.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have gone easy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,00:12:05.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Those girls have promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,00:12:06.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,00:12:11.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They're still blockheads.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,00:12:15.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do with these?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,00:12:23.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,N-no, Koume, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,00:12:26.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You gave me a real hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,00:12:28.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting you get out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,00:12:30.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-I said no! Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,00:12:35.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't move. Let me do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.45,00:12:42.12,Caption,,0,0,0,,NAPPING
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.45,00:12:42.12,Caption2,,0,0,0,,in preparation
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,00:12:42.12,Caption3,,0,0,0,,for night work
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,00:12:42.12,Caption4,,0,0,0,,Don't wake me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,00:12:36.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,00:12:39.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's okay, it won't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,00:12:42.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ah... but I still think...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,00:12:43.45,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Wh-wh-wh-what on Earth is going on \Nin the room next door?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,00:12:45.62,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Wh-wh-wh-what on Earth is going on \Nin the room next door?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,00:12:45.62,Subtitle3,,0,0,0,,Relax a little more. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,00:12:47.00,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Should I stop them? \NRelax a little more. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,00:12:47.37,Subtitle3,,0,0,0,,It's our duty to guide young women \Ndown a wholesome path... \NRelax a little more. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,00:12:50.95,Subtitle3,,0,0,0,,It's our duty to guide young women \Ndown a wholesome path... \NJust like that, just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,00:12:51.12,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,It's our duty to guide young women \Ndown a wholesome path...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,00:12:54.04,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,No, but... but... \NAh- No, please, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,00:12:55.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,00:12:57.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,00:13:00.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.79,00:13:06.58,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,My goodness! You were making those... those... \Nconfusing sounds just because her hair got tangled?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,00:13:09.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What was confusing about them, Saku-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,00:13:11.91,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Huh?! No, uh... \NStaaaare...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,00:13:13.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't get it untangled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,00:13:16.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't rush, just take your time and it'll come off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,00:13:18.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.16,00:13:19.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,00:13:20.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,00:13:23.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Chiya, could you pass those vegetables?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,00:13:24.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,00:13:26.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here, say ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,00:13:29.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait, I can do it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,00:13:35.25,Caption,,0,0,0,,Saku Vision
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,00:13:33.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's okay, it won't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,00:13:35.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ah, Chiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,00:13:37.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Y-you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,00:13:41.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My, what's wrong, Saku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.91,00:13:45.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Chiya's hair is just too long in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.87,00:13:47.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,00:13:49.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well, this is a good opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,00:13:52.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come over here, Chiya, I'll cut it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,00:13:53.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,SCISSORS?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,00:13:55.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wh-what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,00:13:57.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They awakened Chiya's animal instincts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.45,00:14:02.37,Caption,,0,0,0,,BEAST
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.45,00:14:02.37,Caption2,,0,0,0,,MODE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,00:14:02.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No! I'm gonna fall, I'm gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.58,00:14:04.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,C-calm down, Chiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,00:14:06.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Good girl, good girl, good girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,00:14:09.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She's been acting like this for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,00:14:12.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why? Is there a reason she doesn't want to cut it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,00:14:15.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,CUT IT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,00:14:18.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sh-she's really a feral child...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,00:14:21.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Chiya-chan's very difficult to handle today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,00:14:23.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She's acting like a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,00:14:26.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Her stubbornness is such a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.29,00:14:27.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,00:14:30.37,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Rather than cutting her hair, why don't we \Ncut the button off your top, Koume?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,00:14:34.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No way! I really like this top!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,00:14:39.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Who's the one acting like a little kid again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,00:14:46.04,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Chiya doesn't want to cut her hair \Nand Koume doesn't want to hurt her clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,00:14:48.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This certainly isn't going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,00:14:51.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,00:14:55.58,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,This top was made in France, \Nand it's really important to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,00:14:57.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's no way I could cut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,00:15:00.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's no way I could cut mine, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,00:15:03.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well, they do say a woman's hair is her livelihood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,00:15:07.45,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,And, because hair is still alive \Neven after it's cut away from the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.58,00:15:10.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,it's regarded as a symbol of the soul or life energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,00:15:15.58,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,It's closely connected to fortune-telling and spellcasting, \Nand it's very important to an Urara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,00:15:17.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,00:15:19.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nina-sensei, you're so smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,00:15:20.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.79,00:15:23.95,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,So that's why Matsuko-san's hair was always \Ngrowing longer without me realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,00:15:25.41,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,So that's why Matsuko-san's hair was always \Ngrowing longer without me realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,00:15:25.41,Subtitle3,,0,0,0,,Grow... Grow... Grow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,00:15:27.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Scary, scary, scary, scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,00:15:31.83,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, \NSaku-chan had long hair back in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,00:15:34.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, yeah, a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,00:15:41.41,Caption,,0,0,0,,Saku
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,00:15:41.41,Caption2,,0,0,0,,(Age 16)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,00:15:39.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Long hair would look so good on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,00:15:41.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why'd you cut it all off?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,00:15:43.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I cut it when I became a patrol officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,00:15:47.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I vowed to protect Meirocho with my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,00:15:50.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Cutting my hair was proof of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.16,00:15:51.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,00:15:53.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sounds like something you'd do, Saku-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,00:15:57.25,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Though you're a protector, \Nyou're often protected yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,00:16:01.95,Caption,,0,0,0,,Captain Saku
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,00:16:01.95,Caption2,,0,0,0,,FAN CLUB
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,00:15:58.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright, stay back, stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,00:15:59.50,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Alright, stay back, stay back! \NSaku-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,00:16:00.66,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Don't bother Captain Saku while she's hard at work! \NSaku-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,00:16:01.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't bother Captain Saku while she's hard at work!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,00:16:06.41,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,We'll protect Captain Saku from the moment she wakes \Nto the moment she falls asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.70,00:16:08.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right, Captain Saku?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,00:16:10.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,00:16:14.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How did her hair get this tangled up anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.25,00:16:16.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's what I wanna know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,00:16:20.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They say that hair has the power of attraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,00:16:23.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That tied-up hair is like the ties of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,00:16:25.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Tied-up hair is like the ties of fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,00:16:26.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,00:16:31.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is proof of the deep bond between you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,00:16:34.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The deep bond...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.37,00:16:36.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well, nothing we can do, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,00:16:40.79,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,As long as Chiya doesn't wanna cut her hair, \Nwe're gonna have to stay like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,00:16:42.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Koume!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,00:16:45.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'd say they're connected by reins, not by bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,00:16:47.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Will those two be alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,00:16:48.79,Caption,,0,0,0,,BONDS!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,00:16:51.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's hard to move like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.33,00:16:53.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Try not to bump into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,00:16:54.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,00:16:55.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Water, water...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,00:16:59.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Who knows the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,00:17:00.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,00:17:05.70,Caption,,0,0,0,,BATHROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,00:17:03.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,H-hey, Chiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,00:17:05.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you seriously going to follow me EVERYWHERE?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,00:17:08.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can't get untangled, what else can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,00:17:10.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.66,00:17:12.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wh-what are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,00:17:14.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop! Don't come in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,00:17:16.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go on the count of three!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,00:17:18.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's not the problem here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,00:17:24.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well? Have your bonds grown stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,00:17:26.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've grown stronger from the injuries all over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,00:17:29.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I have a favor to ask of you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.41,00:17:31.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Could you go on an errand this evening?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,00:17:34.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh? But we still haven't gotten untangled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.75,00:17:36.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,00:17:39.91,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Your bonds will grow stronger \Nby staying so close to one another!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,00:17:40.87,Caption,,0,0,0,,Staying
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,00:17:40.87,Caption2,,0,0,0,,Close!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,00:17:43.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Chiya, you just stepped on my foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,00:17:45.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're a really fast walker!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,00:17:46.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's MY fault?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.91,00:17:48.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Match your footsteps to mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,00:17:50.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You match mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,00:17:56.62,Caption,,0,0,0,,Sweets
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,00:17:56.62,Caption2,,0,0,0,,ARINSU
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,00:17:56.62,Caption3,,0,0,0,,Caf√©
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,00:17:56.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Piping hot sakura manju here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.70,00:18:02.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Of course we'd inevitably get a little irritated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,00:18:05.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But that means it's the perfect time to eat some sweets!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,00:18:07.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thiff ivv Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,00:18:13.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chiya, why are you so against cutting your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.91,00:18:17.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,C'mon, lemme hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.62,00:18:19.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,00:18:22.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Jeez, why're you keeping it a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,00:18:25.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I just don't wanna say why!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,00:18:27.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,God, you're so stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,00:18:32.00,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,But honestly, when I think about it, \NChiya really is one mystery after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.83,00:18:35.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She's a harebrained girl who grew up in the mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,00:18:38.83,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,and she doesn't know anything \Nabout Urara or living in a town...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,00:18:44.95,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,She's reckless and naive, and she always \Nlooks like she's not afraid of anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,00:18:49.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I really don't know anything else about Chiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,00:18:53.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Even though she's so physically close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,00:18:58.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is proof of the deep bond between you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,00:19:00.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nina-sensei, you liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.83,00:19:02.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Koume?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,00:19:05.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Chiya, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,00:19:07.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You can just tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,00:19:09.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know we've only just met each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,00:19:12.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but the way we met might've been some kind of fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,00:19:16.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And we're both students at Natsumeya, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,00:19:18.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,W-we're already friends, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.87,00:19:21.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.75,00:19:23.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A lovers' quarrel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.29,00:19:24.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They're taking off their clothes and getting close, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,00:19:27.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,L-let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,00:19:30.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, we wanna pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,00:19:33.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait, Koume!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,00:19:36.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are we really friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.83,00:19:38.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why would I lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,00:19:41.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then Nono and Kon are friends, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,00:19:44.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's right! Everyone thinks so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,00:19:48.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And friends wanna know more about each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,00:19:50.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's just, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,00:19:51.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,00:19:53.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy, Koume!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,00:19:57.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you for saying we're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,00:20:03.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,O-of course we're friends, but we're also students,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,00:20:05.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,wh-which makes us rivals, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,00:20:06.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,00:20:09.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We're colleagues, friends, and rivals!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,00:20:11.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We're so busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,00:20:15.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Jeez, you don't have to get so close to me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.62,00:20:17.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Chiya, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,00:20:21.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm glad her hair came out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.00,00:20:28.16,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,This high-quality camellia oil will make your hair hurt less, \Nand keep it from tangling so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,00:20:30.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Since you're both here, we'll do it for you too, Koume.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,00:20:35.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It feels weird for only us to be in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,00:20:41.62,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,My, but the princesses in the olden days had many \Nladies-in-waiting who would wash their hair for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.62,00:20:42.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,00:20:45.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Those princesses sure lived a luxurious life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.75,00:20:47.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,00:20:49.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's give it a little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.12,00:20:57.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Koume, will you hear me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,00:21:00.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wanna tell you why I don't wanna cut my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,00:21:05.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When I was really little...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,00:21:07.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Setsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.04,00:21:09.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's for dinner today?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,00:21:11.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,00:21:14.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Chiya, don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,00:21:18.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We've got a real feast today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,00:21:20.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna make roasted white snake tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.83,00:21:24.50,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,We don't get to have this often at all! How lucky! \NSob, sob... Sob, sob!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.50,00:21:25.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sob, sob... Sob, sob!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,00:21:26.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A-and ever since,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,00:21:28.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've been so, so, so, so scared that if I cut my hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,00:21:31.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,blood's gonna go everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,00:21:31.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's why I didn't wanna say why either!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,00:21:33.08,Subtitle3,,0,0,0,,The traumatic experience is so wild \NI can barely wrap my head around it. \NThat's why I didn't wanna say why either!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,00:21:35.91,Subtitle3,,0,0,0,,The traumatic experience is so wild \NI can barely wrap my head around it. \NA-and I'm so, so, so, so scared of scissors, too...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.91,00:21:36.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A-and I'm so, so, so, so scared of scissors, too...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.29,00:21:41.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's so not like you to be afraid of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.37,00:21:43.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.33,00:21:45.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, Koume...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,00:21:48.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wanna know more about you and everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.08,00:21:51.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The stuff you're scared of and the stuff you like, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,00:21:53.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We all met one another, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,00:21:56.79,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll tell you anything \Nyou want to know from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.87,00:22:03.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is this really Chiya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.54,00:22:06.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She's sparkling so much, I can barely believe it's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,00:22:09.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Chiya-chan looks like a real princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.62,00:22:11.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Now there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,00:22:13.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Nina-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.12,00:22:13.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.37,00:22:16.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's start preparing dinner, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,00:22:18.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nono, could you please clean that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,00:22:19.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.41,00:22:25.37,Caption,,0,0,0,,RAWRRRR
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.33,00:22:24.79,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,She went from a high-class pedigree \Nto a stray mutt in two seconds flat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.79,00:22:27.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Jeez, cut it out already! Chiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.62,00:22:50.50,Song,,0,0,0,,If I turn the corner, I wonder if I'll reach my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.04,00:22:55.20,Song,,0,0,0,,Getting lost and wandering in circles
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,00:22:59.04,Song,,0,0,0,,It'd be great if I could just run into you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.04,00:23:03.75,Song,,0,0,0,,There are some days when I don't have it altogether 1 to 10
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,00:23:07.04,Song,,0,0,0,,Which way should I go to get a happy ending?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.41,00:23:12.20,Song,,0,0,0,,From right to left, from like to love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.20,00:23:14.91,Song,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh, I'm in love with love! I'm in such a hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.91,00:23:18.95,Song,,0,0,0,,I want it badly, I can't get out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.33,00:23:23.29,Song,,0,0,0,,I'm looking
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.29,00:23:25.41,Song,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.41,00:23:27.75,Song,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen what you look like, but my heart's beating fast
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.75,00:23:29.79,Song,,0,0,0,,Kiss me in my imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.79,00:23:31.91,Song,,0,0,0,,The moment we meet is a crash
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,00:23:34.04,Song,,0,0,0,,It gets a little complicated, that's fate
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.04,00:23:38.16,Song,,0,0,0,,Maybe, maybe you're lost too?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.29,00:23:40.91,Song,,0,0,0,,We can't see the end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.91,00:23:45.91,Song,,0,0,0,,The maze that starts with romance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.20,00:23:51.08,Song,,0,0,0,,Will you find me in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.20,00:24:06.75,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Next time on Urara Meirocho, \N"Good and Bad Things are Sometimes Ticklish"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.87,00:24:10.83,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,We'll use dice fortune-telling to see \Nwhat kind of episode it'll be, Chiya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.95,00:24:11.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Rah!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.58,00:24:14.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The dice are stuck in the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.29,00:24:16.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,"Good and Bad Things
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.29,00:24:16.04,Caption2,,0,0,0,,are Sometimes Ticklish"
